{"title":"打造並美化終端機和 Vim 編輯器","uid":"dbc07921d26fb2dbbbe164cfe2d50397","slug":"terminal-beautify-tutorial","date":"2023-01-04T04:51:39.000Z","updated":"2023-01-04T10:12:25.095Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/terminal-beautify-tutorial.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<div class=\"custom-quote warning\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 15.99V16.01\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">注意</p>\n<p>本文章需要使用 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://brew.sh/index_zh-tw\">Homebrew</a>，請先把其安裝。</p>\n</div>\n<p>基本上，我們都不會再用 MacOS 預設的 Terminal 軟件，取而的是 iTerm2，與較原始的 Terminal 比較，這個<strong>提供更多進階功能和設定</strong>。</p>\n<p>可到這裏安裝 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://iterm2.com/downloads.html\">iTerm2</a> 軟件包，或輸入指令安裝：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">brew cask install iterm2</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"為終端機設定真實色\"><a href=\"#為終端機設定真實色\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"為終端機設定真實色\"></a>為終端機設定真實色</h1><p>安裝 iTerm2 原因其中之一，是能夠支援真實色（全彩 - 256色），真實色可以<strong>使終端機顯示更漂亮的色彩配置</strong>。</p>\n<p>點擊 <kbd class=\"menu\">iTerm2</kbd> 選單 &gt; <kbd class=\"menu\">Settings</kbd> &gt; <kbd class=\"menu\">Profiles</kbd> &gt; <kbd class=\"menu\">Terminal</kbd></p>\n<p>把 <kbd class=\"menu\">Report terminal type</kbd> 並設定為 <code>xterm-256color</code>。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/post/terminal-beautify-tutorial/img1.png\" alt=\"img1\"></p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"為終端機設定色彩主題\"><a href=\"#為終端機設定色彩主題\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"為終端機設定色彩主題\"></a>為終端機設定色彩主題</h1><p><strong>你的終端機不是黑白就是像駭客</strong>，想要得到這個終端機的外觀？那就繼續看下去！</p>\n<p><img src=\"/post/terminal-beautify-tutorial/img2.png\" alt=\"img2\"></p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">小提示</p>\n<p>這個輸出是 <code>neofetch</code> 指令生成的。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">brew install neofetch</code></pre>\n\n</p>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"基本主題配置\"><a href=\"#基本主題配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"基本主題配置\"></a>基本主題配置</h2><p><img src=\"/post/terminal-beautify-tutorial/img3.png\" alt=\"img3\"></p>\n<p>Terminal 或 ITerm2 提供了一些內建主題，在 <kbd class=\"menu\">Profiles</kbd> &gt; <kbd class=\"menu\">Colors</kbd> &gt; <kbd class=\"menu\">Color Preset</kbd> 那裏可以選擇主題，如果還想發掘其他更美的主題，可到 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/mbadolato/iTerm2-Color-Schemes\">iTerm2-Color-Schemes</a> 下載其他主題。</p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">小提示</p>\n<ol>\n<li>前往 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/mbadolato/iTerm2-Color-Schemes\">iTerm2-Color-Schemes</a> 後，點擊 Code &gt; Download ZIP 把所有檔案以壓縮檔下載至你的電腦。</li>\n<li>點擊 <kbd class=\"menu\">iTerm2</kbd> 選單 &gt; <kbd class=\"menu\">Settings</kbd> &gt; <kbd class=\"menu\">Profiles</kbd> &gt; <kbd class=\"menu\">Colors</kbd> &gt; <kbd class=\"menu\">Color Preset</kbd> &gt; <kbd class=\"menu\">Import</kbd>。</li>\n<li>找 <code>schemes</code> 資料夾，裏面有一系列的主題 (<code>.itermcolors</code> 檔案用於匯入並應用 iTerm2 主題檔案)</li>\n<li>點擊確定後關閉 iTerm2 - <kbd>Cmd</kbd> + <kbd>Q</kbd> 並重啟。</li>\n</ol>\n\n</div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"進階主題配置\"><a href=\"#進階主題配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"進階主題配置\"></a>進階主題配置</h2><hr>\n<h3 id=\"安裝-zsh\"><a href=\"#安裝-zsh\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安裝 zsh\"></a>安裝 zsh</h3><div class=\"custom-quote danger\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M19.76 5.23C15.84 5.23 12 2 12 2C12 2 8.15996 5.23 4.23996 5.23C4.23996 5.23 1.86996 16.99 12 22C22.13 16.99 19.76 5.23 19.76 5.23Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 16H12\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">特别注意</p>\n<p>自 <strong>Mac OS 10 (MacOS Catalina)</strong> 版本起，終端機<strong>預設</strong>不再以 <code>bash</code>，取而代之是<strong>以 <code>zsh</code> 作為殼層</strong>。</p>\n</div>\n<p>不過你也可以檢查一下有沒有安裝 <code>zsh</code>。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">which zsh</code></pre>\n\n<p>如果沒有，可以手動安裝：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">brew install zsh\nsudo sh -c &quot;echo $(which zsh) &gt;&gt; &#x2F;etc&#x2F;shells&quot;</code></pre>\n\n<p>把 <code>zsh</code> 設為預設殼層。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">chsh -s $(which zsh)</code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"custom-quote danger\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M19.76 5.23C15.84 5.23 12 2 12 2C12 2 8.15996 5.23 4.23996 5.23C4.23996 5.23 1.86996 16.99 12 22C22.13 16.99 19.76 5.23 19.76 5.23Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 16H12\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">特别注意</p>\n<p>用 Homebrew 安裝的 <code>zsh</code> 位置在 <code>/usr/local/bin/zsh</code>；<br>系統安裝的 <code>zsh</code> 位置在 <code>/bin/zsh</code>。</p>\n<p>在首次安裝 <code>zsh</code> 的時候會進入 <code>zsh</code> 設定界面，建議<strong>依照 Recommended 的提示</strong>進行設定。</p>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"安裝-oh-my-zsh\"><a href=\"#安裝-oh-my-zsh\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安裝 oh-my-zsh\"></a>安裝 oh-my-zsh</h3><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>不是 oh my god，但一旦你把它安裝到終端機，或許你會有這個反應！</p></blockquote>\n<p>須知 <code>zsh</code> 使用繁複，先不說調整設定，光是初始化也要使用很多腦載量，安裝到一半可能就棄械投降，所以 <code>zsh</code> 在<strong>初期甚少得到賞識</strong>。不過，今時今日，現在我們可以用 <code>oh-my-zsh</code> ，它是一個讓 <code>zsh</code> <strong>更容易使用的套件</strong>！</p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">小提示</p>\n<p>大部分的 <code>zsh</code> 套件都支援 <code>oh-my-zsh</code>。</p>\n</div>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">sh -c &quot;$(curl -fsSL https:&#x2F;&#x2F;raw.github.com&#x2F;ohmyzsh&#x2F;ohmyzsh&#x2F;master&#x2F;tools&#x2F;install.sh)&quot;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"設定-zsh-主題\"><a href=\"#設定-zsh-主題\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"設定 zsh 主題\"></a>設定 zsh 主題</h3><p><code>oh-my-zsh</code> 提供了許多主題，例如在 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh\">oh-my-zsh 官方文案</a> 看到的 <code>robbyrussell</code>、<code>agnoster</code> 主題。我們可以透過文本編輯修改 <code>~/.zshrc</code> 檔案內容，從而應用想要的主題。</p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">小提示</p>\n<p><code>.zshrc</code> 是修改 <code>zsh</code> 設定的核心檔案。</p>\n</div>\n<p>開啟 <code>~/.zshrc</code>。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">vi ~&#x2F;.zshrc</code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"custom-quote danger\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M19.76 5.23C15.84 5.23 12 2 12 2C12 2 8.15996 5.23 4.23996 5.23C4.23996 5.23 1.86996 16.99 12 22C22.13 16.99 19.76 5.23 19.76 5.23Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 16H12\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">特别注意</p>\n<p>當文件打開後，會進入命令模式，這個時候<strong>當你敲擊鍵盤的一些作用鍵會被辨別為命令</strong>，而不是輸入字元，要按鍵盤 I 鍵進入插入模式。</p>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">小提示</p>\n<p>進入插入模式 - <kbd>I</kbd><br>進入底線命令模式 - <kbd>:</kbd><br>退出輸入模式，並切換命令模式 - <kbd>ESC</kbd><br>複製所選字元 - <kbd>Y</kbd><br>貼上已複製字元 - <kbd>P</kbd><br>剪下所選字元 - <kbd>D</kbd><br>復原 (Undo) - <kbd>U</kbd><br>重做 (Redo) - <kbd>Ctrl</kbd> + <kbd>R</kbd><br>召喚自動完成選單 - <kbd>Ctrl</kbd> + <kbd>N</kbd></p>\n\n</div>\n<hr>\n<p>在 <code>~/.zshrc</code> 檔案內，找 <code>ZSH_THEME</code> 設定。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-vim\" data-language=\"vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">ZSH_THEME&#x3D;&quot;robbyrussell&quot;</code></pre>\n\n<p><code>robbyrussell</code> 是 zsh 預設應用的主題，如果你想要使用其他，可到 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/tree/master/themes\">這裏</a> 看所有主題，<code>.zsh-theme</code> 副檔名的檔案是用於 <code>ZSH_THEME</code> 設定。</p>\n<p>例如是 <code>sunshine.zsh-theme</code>：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-vim\" data-language=\"vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">ZSH_THEME&#x3D;&quot;sunshine&quot;</code></pre>\n\n<p>重啟殼層更新設定。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">exec $SHELL</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"安裝-Powerlevel10k\"><a href=\"#安裝-Powerlevel10k\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安裝 Powerlevel10k\"></a>安裝 Powerlevel10k</h3><p>來到這裏，如果 <code>oh-my-zsh</code> 已經足夠讓你感到 oh my god 的話，你可以住手了。但是，我們將會進一步利用強大 <code>zsh</code> 主題美化終端機，它就是 <code>Powerlevel10k</code>。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><code>Powerlevel10k</code> 是 <code>Powerlevel9k</code> 的新一代版本。</p></blockquote>\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">更新特點：</p>\n<p><ul>\n<li>人性化的<strong>引導式</strong>設定界面</li>\n<li><strong>不用自行安裝</strong> Powerline 字體</li>\n<li>更多命令行客製化設定</li>\n</ul>\n<p>如果你安裝過 <code>Powerlevel9k</code>，不用擔心，兩者版本的設定相容，但 <code>Powerlevel10k</code> 更優，建議更新。</p>\n</p>\n</div>\n<p>我們會透過 <code>oh-my-zsh</code> 安裝 <code>Powerlevel10k</code>。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">git clone --depth&#x3D;1 https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;romkatv&#x2F;powerlevel10k.git $&#123;ZSH_CUSTOM:-$HOME&#x2F;.oh-my-zsh&#x2F;custom&#125;&#x2F;themes&#x2F;powerlevel10k</code></pre>\n\n<p>同樣用 <code>vi</code> ，設定主題為 <code>powerlevel10k</code>。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">vi ~&#x2F;.zshrc</code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-vim\" data-language=\"vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">ZSH_THEME&#x3D;&quot;powerlevel10k&#x2F;powerlevel10k&quot;</code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"custom-quote danger\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M19.76 5.23C15.84 5.23 12 2 12 2C12 2 8.15996 5.23 4.23996 5.23C4.23996 5.23 1.86996 16.99 12 22C22.13 16.99 19.76 5.23 19.76 5.23Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 16H12\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">特别注意</p>\n<p>如果你不是用 <code>oh-my-zsh</code> 安裝 <code>Powerlevel10k</code>，而把以上設定設置到 <code>.zshrc</code>，會報錯。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">[oh-my-zsh] theme &#39;powerlevel10k&#x2F;powerlevel10k&#39; not found</code></pre>\n\n<p>這個時候，重新安裝 <code>oh-my-zsh</code> 和 <code>Powerlevel10k</code>。</p>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<p>重啟終端機或輸入指令進入 <code>Powerlevel10k</code> 設定界面：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">p10k configure</code></pre>\n\n<p>照着畫面一步步選擇你喜歡的設定便可以。</p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote danger\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M19.76 5.23C15.84 5.23 12 2 12 2C12 2 8.15996 5.23 4.23996 5.23C4.23996 5.23 1.86996 16.99 12 22C22.13 16.99 19.76 5.23 19.76 5.23Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 16H12\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">特别注意</p>\n<ol>\n<li>如果它詢問你 <code>Does this look like a diamond (rotated square)?</code> 或類似問題的時候，<strong>與你所見並不一致</strong>，這個很可能<strong>你沒有安裝 Powerline 字體</strong>。</li>\n<li>如果它沒有詢問 <code>Install Meslo Nerd Font?</code> 的話，<strong>重裝 <code>Powerlevel10k</code></strong> 試試。</li>\n<li>如果你要很多花俏的圖示，<code>Character Set</code> 要選 <code>Unicode</code>。</li>\n<li><code>Transient Prompt</code> 是 <code>Powerlevel10k</code> 新功能，會讓命令行固定只有一個，每次<strong>輸入完指令和輸出歷史會自動往上印</strong>。</li>\n</ol>\n\n</div>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"使用-Plugin-manager-進階功能配置\"><a href=\"#使用-Plugin-manager-進階功能配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用 Plugin manager 進階功能配置\"></a>使用 Plugin manager 進階功能配置</h1><div class=\"custom-quote warning\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 15.99V16.01\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">注意</p>\n<p>用 <code>oh-my-zsh</code> 安裝。</p>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"啟用輸入指令時的語法突顯\"><a href=\"#啟用輸入指令時的語法突顯\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"啟用輸入指令時的語法突顯\"></a>啟用輸入指令時的語法突顯</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">git clone https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;zsh-users&#x2F;zsh-syntax-highlighting.git $&#123;ZSH_CUSTOM:-~&#x2F;.oh-my-zsh&#x2F;custom&#125;&#x2F;plugins&#x2F;zsh-syntax-highlighting</code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-vim\" data-language=\"vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">plugins&#x3D;(\n    # ...\n    zsh-syntax-highlighting\n)</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"啟用輸入指令時自動完成提示\"><a href=\"#啟用輸入指令時自動完成提示\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"啟用輸入指令時自動完成提示\"></a>啟用輸入指令時自動完成提示</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">git clone https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;zsh-users&#x2F;zsh-autosuggestions $&#123;ZSH_CUSTOM:-~&#x2F;.oh-my-zsh&#x2F;custom&#125;&#x2F;plugins&#x2F;zsh-autosuggestions</code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-vim\" data-language=\"vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">plugins&#x3D;( \n    # ...\n    zsh-autosuggestions\n)</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"Vim-編輯器外觀設定\"><a href=\"#Vim-編輯器外觀設定\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Vim 編輯器外觀設定\"></a>Vim 編輯器外觀設定</h1><p>把終端機弄美後，是不是都很想有股衝動美化 Vim 編輯器呢？這部分就是教大家怎樣將 Vim 編輯器像我的一樣美。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/post/terminal-beautify-tutorial/img4.png\" alt=\"img4\"></p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote warning\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 15.99V16.01\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">注意</p>\n<p>如果你沒有安裝 <code>vim</code>，可以用 Homebrew 安裝：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">brew install vim</code></pre>\n\n<p><code>vim</code> 與 <code>vi</code> 有什麼區別？Vim 是 <strong>Vi iMproved</strong>，簡而言之就是<strong>改善並把 Vi 編輯器功能進階化</strong>。</p>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">小提示</p>\n<p>建議安裝 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://macvim-dev.github.io/macvim/\">MacVim</a>，好處：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>MacVim 是一個獨立軟件，可以把<strong>檔案直接拖拽並直接打開</strong>。</li>\n<li>可以<strong>用 Mac OS 建有的快捷鍵</strong>，如 <kbd>Cmd</kbd> + <kbd>X</kbd>。</li>\n</ol>\n</p>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"安裝-vim-plug\"><a href=\"#安裝-vim-plug\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安裝 vim-plug\"></a>安裝 vim-plug</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">curl -fLo ~&#x2F;.vim&#x2F;autoload&#x2F;plug.vim --create-dirs \\\n    https:&#x2F;&#x2F;raw.githubusercontent.com&#x2F;junegunn&#x2F;vim-plug&#x2F;master&#x2F;plug.vim</code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">vim ~&#x2F;.vimrc</code></pre>\n\n<p>在 <code>.vimrc</code> 內加入編碼：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-vim\" data-language=\"vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">call plug#begin()\n\ncall plug#end()</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"Vim-插件\"><a href=\"#Vim-插件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Vim 插件\"></a>Vim 插件</h2><p>加入插件：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-vim\" data-language=\"vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">call plug#begin()\nPlug &#39;...&#39;\ncall plug#end()</code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"custom-quote danger\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M19.76 5.23C15.84 5.23 12 2 12 2C12 2 8.15996 5.23 4.23996 5.23C4.23996 5.23 1.86996 16.99 12 22C22.13 16.99 19.76 5.23 19.76 5.23Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 16H12\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">特别注意</p>\n<p><code>Plug &#39;...&#39;</code> 只是樣板，<strong>別把它運行，會報錯</strong>，接下來會使用插件。</p>\n<p>把插件加入後要做的步驟：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><code>:qw</code> - <kbd>ESC</kbd> + <kbd>:</kbd> + <kbd>Q</kbd> + <kbd>W</kbd> 儲存。</li>\n<li><code>:PlugInstall</code> - <kbd>ESC</kbd> + <kbd>:</kbd> + <code>PlugInstall</code>。</li>\n<li>重啟 <code>vim</code>。</li>\n</ol>\n</p>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"airline-amp-airline-themes\"><a href=\"#airline-amp-airline-themes\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"airline &amp; airline-themes\"></a>airline &amp; airline-themes</h3><p><img src=\"/post/terminal-beautify-tutorial/img5.png\" alt=\"img5\"><br><img src=\"/post/terminal-beautify-tutorial/img6.png\" alt=\"img6\"><br><img src=\"/post/terminal-beautify-tutorial/img7.png\" alt=\"img7\"><br><img src=\"/post/terminal-beautify-tutorial/img8.png\" alt=\"img8\"><br><img src=\"/post/terminal-beautify-tutorial/img9.png\" alt=\"img9\"></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-vim\" data-language=\"vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">call plug#begin()\nPlug &#39;vim-airline&#x2F;vim-airline&#39;\nPlug &#39;vim-airline&#x2F;vim-airline-themes&#39;\ncall plug#end()</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"安裝-Vim-主題\"><a href=\"#安裝-Vim-主題\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安裝 Vim 主題\"></a>安裝 Vim 主題</h3><hr>\n<h4 id=\"安裝-material-vim\"><a href=\"#安裝-material-vim\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安裝 material.vim\"></a>安裝 material.vim</h4><p>在這教學，我們會用 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/kaicataldo/material.vim\">material.vim</a> 主題，如果你要用其他，就要依從該主題的安裝方法。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kaicataldo/material.vim/main/screenshots/material-all-variants.png\" alt=\"githubImg\"></p>\n<p>安裝 <code>material.vim</code>：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-vim\" data-language=\"vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">Plug &#39;kaicataldo&#x2F;material.vim&#39;, &#123; &#39;branch&#39;: &#39;main&#39; &#125;</code></pre>\n\n<p>應用 <code>material</code> 主題。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-vim\" data-language=\"vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">colorscheme material</code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"custom-quote danger\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M19.76 5.23C15.84 5.23 12 2 12 2C12 2 8.15996 5.23 4.23996 5.23C4.23996 5.23 1.86996 16.99 12 22C22.13 16.99 19.76 5.23 19.76 5.23Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 16H12\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">特别注意</p>\n<p>所有經過插件擴充的設定值，如 <code>colorscheme material</code> 內的 <code>material</code>，是來自 <code>kaicataldo/material.vim</code> 的，所以<strong>設定值要在 <code>Plug</code> 區塊後才能使用</strong>。</p>\n<p>即是：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-vim\" data-language=\"vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">call plug#begin()\nPlug &#39;kaicataldo&#x2F;material.vim&#39;, &#123; &#39;branch&#39;: &#39;main&#39; &#125;\ncall plug#end()\n\ncolorscheme material</code></pre>\n\n</p>\n</div>\n<h4 id=\"為-Vim-設定真實色\"><a href=\"#為-Vim-設定真實色\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"為 Vim 設定真實色\"></a>為 Vim 設定真實色</h4><p>在 <code>.vimrc</code> 內加入編碼：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-vim\" data-language=\"vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">if (has(&#39;nvim&#39;))\n  let $NVIM_TUI_ENABLE_TRUE_COLOR &#x3D; 1\nendif\nif has(&quot;termguicolors&quot;)\n    &quot; fix bug for vim\n    set t_8f&#x3D;^[[38;2;%lu;%lu;%lum\n    set t_8b&#x3D;^[[48;2;%lu;%lu;%lum\n    &quot; enable true color\n    set termguicolors\nendif</code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"設定-Material-主題\"><a href=\"#設定-Material-主題\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"設定 Material 主題\"></a>設定 Material 主題</h4><p>material.vim 一共設有 10 款 Material 主題，其中 5 款為 Community Material 主題。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Lighter &#x2F; Community Lighter</li>\n<li>Darker &#x2F; Community Darker</li>\n<li>Palenight &#x2F; Community Palenight</li>\n<li>Ocean &#x2F; Community Ocean</li>\n<li>Default &#x2F; Community Default</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">小提示</p>\n<p>按照 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://material-theme.com/docs/reference/color-palette/\">Material 主題調色</a>，Default 即是 Oceanic，而 Ocean 即是 Deep Ocean。</p>\n</div>\n<p>這裏是主題的所有可設定值：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-vim\" data-language=\"vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">let g:material_theme_style &#x3D; &#39;default&#39; | &#39;palenight&#39; | &#39;ocean&#39; | &#39;lighter&#39; | &#39;darker&#39; | &#39;default-community&#39; | &#39;palenight-community&#39; | &#39;ocean-community&#39; | &#39;lighter-community&#39; | &#39;darker-community&#39;</code></pre>\n\n<p>例如我想要 Community Material 主題（即是我一開始展示的那一個）。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-vim\" data-language=\"vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">set background&#x3D;dark\n\nlet g:material_theme_style &#x3D; &#39;palenight-community&#39;\ncolorscheme material</code></pre>\n\n<p>如果你想要斜體如<strong>註釋</strong>斜體的語法突顯：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-vim\" data-language=\"vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">let g:material_terminal_italics &#x3D; 1</code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"custom-quote danger\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M19.76 5.23C15.84 5.23 12 2 12 2C12 2 8.15996 5.23 4.23996 5.23C4.23996 5.23 1.86996 16.99 12 22C22.13 16.99 19.76 5.23 19.76 5.23Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 16H12\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">特别注意</p>\n<p>這個設定<strong>不會把所有字元都轉為斜體</strong>，它把字元轉為斜體是<strong>按語法主題文件而定</strong>的。</p>\n<p>如果你設定了斜體後<strong>斜體字元有背景顏色</strong>的話，你可以試試在 <code>colorscheme</code> 那行往下加入編碼：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-vim\" data-language=\"vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">&quot; fix italics in Vim\nif !has(&#39;nvim&#39;)\n  let &amp;t_ZH&#x3D;&quot;\\e[3m&quot;\n  let &amp;t_ZR&#x3D;&quot;\\e[23m&quot;\nendif</code></pre>\n\n<p>如果你設定了主題後<strong>沒有語法突顯色彩</strong>，可能你沒為 Vim 啟用語法突顯：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-vim\" data-language=\"vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">syntax on</code></pre>\n\n</p>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"Vim-其他設定\"><a href=\"#Vim-其他設定\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Vim 其他設定\"></a>Vim 其他設定</h1><hr>\n<h2 id=\"自動進入插入模式\"><a href=\"#自動進入插入模式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"自動進入插入模式\"></a>自動進入插入模式</h2><p>開啟 Vim 編輯器後自動進入插入模式（Insert mode）。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-vim\" data-language=\"vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">start</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"鼠標點擊控制\"><a href=\"#鼠標點擊控制\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"鼠標點擊控制\"></a>鼠標點擊控制</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-vim\" data-language=\"vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">set mouse&#x3D;a</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"啟用行號\"><a href=\"#啟用行號\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"啟用行號\"></a>啟用行號</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-vim\" data-language=\"vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">set number</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"啟用語法突顯\"><a href=\"#啟用語法突顯\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"啟用語法突顯\"></a>啟用語法突顯</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-vim\" data-language=\"vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">syntax on</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"顯示目前行背景顏色\"><a href=\"#顯示目前行背景顏色\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"顯示目前行背景顏色\"></a>顯示目前行背景顏色</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-vim\" data-language=\"vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">set cursorline</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"顯示頂部列和檔案頁籤\"><a href=\"#顯示頂部列和檔案頁籤\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"顯示頂部列和檔案頁籤\"></a>顯示頂部列和檔案頁籤</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-vim\" data-language=\"vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">set showtabline&#x3D;2</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<p>好了，大概就是這樣了。這個是我建立這個 <code>md</code> 檔案的時間，2023-01-04 <strong>12:51</strong>，結果到 <strong>16:10</strong> 才打好這篇文章哈哈。。</p>\n","feature":true,"text":" 注意 本文章需要使用 Homebrew，請先把其安裝。 基本上，我們都不會再用 MacOS 預設的 Terminal 軟件，取而的是 iTerm2，與較原始的 Terminal 比較，這個提供更多進階功能和設定。 可到這裏安裝 iTerm2 軟件包，或輸入指令安裝： brew ...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"6.9k","symbolsTime":"6 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"終端機指令","slug"